rows.label: tev025201_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Nastasha for her thoughts on Elma.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0001
rows.name:
Having to call for reinforcements was a blunder born
from our own mistakes.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0002
rows.name:
But the one silver lining was that the great Elma
herself—or rather, Team Elma—came to save us![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0003
rows.name:
Still, I hope we can keep this a secret from
Commander Vandham?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0004
rows.name:
I know he'd completely blow up at us if he knew.
Probably accuse us of being cocky just because we
managed to fight off the Ganglion.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0010
rows.name: Piers, who guards the west gate, is a really nice guy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0013
rows.name:
He always lets me know when Elma passes through
the west gate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0014
rows.name: Er, it's not like I'm stalking her or anything![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025201_MSG0015
rows.name:
It's just human nature to want to know what the people
you admire are up to, right?[ST:wait ]
